726288f-a.title: Queens: Browvale Drive - Northern Boulevard
726288f-a.text:
Browvale Drive, east side, south from Northern Boulevard,
then turning east. This area is known as Browvale Hills,
Little Neck, "where nature did her best," according to the out-
door sign.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
